to channel something to the warrior to get the DPS. I  live on unpredictability and apart from Vish and to an extent Yar'Lir it's not their . Anguish , apart from OMM, is yawn etc etc etc.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;My 2cp and if someone sat Unmei, Yakk and LordTed in a room with a Dev and made one raid, one group mez and one group charm with Nanyea as mod / contributor nothing will happen.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
